Package: reprextemplates
Title: Reprex Media Asset Templates And Utilities
Version: 0.1.19
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniel", "Antal", 
           email = "daniel.antal@dataobservatory.eu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7513-6760"))
Description: Tools for creating reproducible media assets and supporting 
    file workflows. Includes utilities for concatenating text files, 
    renaming exported assets (e.g. presentation slides), and generating 
    consistent color palettes. Designed to support reproducible reporting, 
    documentation, and lightweight data processing workflows. Developed for 
    Reprex B.V. and collaborating developers and partners.
